## Optional: Persistence Image```


Cell 10:
```
from persim import PersistenceImager

pimgr = PersistenceImager(pixel_size=0.05, birth_range=(0, 1), pers_range=(0, 1))
pimgr.fit(h1)
img = pimgr.transform(h1)

plt.figure(figsize=(5, 5))
pimgr.plot_image(img)
plt.title('Persistence Image (H1)')
plt.show()```

